HEADWORD: Tithonic
<hw>Ti*thon"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Tithonius</ets> belonging to <ets>Tithonus</ets>, the consort of
Aurora, Gr. <?/.]</ety> <def>Of, pertaining to, or denoting, those rays
of light which produce chemical effects; actinic.</def>
